<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>DJ YourName</title>

<style>

body{
font-family:Arial;
margin:0;
background:#0f0f0f;
color:white;
}

header{
background:black;
padding:15px;
position:sticky;
top:0;
}

nav{
display:flex;
justify-content:space-between;
align-items:center;
}

.logo{
font-size:22px;
font-weight:bold;
}

.menu{
list-style:none;
display:flex;
margin:0;
padding:0;
}

.menu li{
position:relative;
}

.menu li a{
color:white;
text-decoration:none;
padding:12px 18px;
display:block;
}

.menu li:hover{
background:#1e1e1e;
}

.dropdown{
display:none;
position:absolute;
background:#111;
top:45px;
min-width:180px;
}

.dropdown a{
display:block;
}

.menu li:hover .dropdown{
display:block;
}

section{
padding:60px 20px;
max-width:1000px;
margin:auto;
}

.hero{
text-align:center;
padding:120px 20px;
background:linear-gradient(black,#111);
}

.hero h1{
font-size:48px;
}

button{
background:#ff0066;
border:none;
padding:12px 20px;
color:white;
font-size:16px;
cursor:pointer;
border-radius:5px;
}

button:hover{
background:#ff2c7f;
}

.card{
background:#151515;
padding:25px;
margin:20px 0;
border-radius:8px;
}

.video-grid{
display:grid;
grid-template-columns:repeat(auto-fit,minmax(250px,1fr));
gap:20px;
}

footer{
text-align:center;
padding:30px;
background:black;
margin-top:40px;
}

input, textarea{
width:100%;
padding:10px;
margin:8px 0;
border:none;
border-radius:4px;
}

</style>
</head>

<body>

<header>

<nav>

<div class="logo">DJ YourName</div>

<ul class="menu">

<li><a href="#">Home</a></li>

<li>
<a href="#">About ▼</a>
<div class="dropdown">
<a href="#bio">Bio</a>
<a href="#social">Social Media</a>
</div>
</li>

<li>
<a href="#">Services ▼</a>
<div class="dropdown">
<a href="#packages">Packages</a>
<a href="#videos">Videos</a>
</div>
</li>

<li>
<a href="#">Bookings ▼</a>
<div class="dropdown">
<a href="#booking">Book Me</a>
<a href="#payments">Payments</a>
</div>
</li>

<li>
<a href="#">Support ▼</a>
<div class="dropdown">
<a href="#support">Tips</a>
<a href="#contact">Contact</a>
</div>
</li>

</ul>

</nav>

</header>

<div class="hero">
<h1>DJ YourName</h1>
<p>Live DJ • Events • Parties • Clubs</p>
<button onclick="document.getElementById('booking').scrollIntoView()">Book Now</button>
</div>

<section id="bio">
<h2>Bio</h2>
<div class="card">
<p>
DJ YourName is a professional DJ specializing in clubs, private events,
and festivals. With years of experience mixing hip-hop, EDM, house,
and open format, every performance delivers high energy and unforgettable vibes.
</p>
</div>
</section>

<section id="social">
<h2>Social Media</h2>
<div class="card">
<p>Follow me:</p>

<p>
Instagram: https://instagram.com/yourname<br>
YouTube: https://youtube.com/yourname<br>
TikTok: https://tiktok.com/@yourname
</p>

</div>
</section>

<section id="videos">
<h2>Videos</h2>

<div class="video-grid">

<iframe height="200" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/VIDEOID"></iframe>

<iframe height="200" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/VIDEOID"></iframe>

<iframe height="200" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/VIDEOID"></iframe>

</div>

</section>

<section id="packages">
<h2>DJ Packages</h2>

<div class="card">
<h3>Basic Party Package</h3>
<p>2 Hour DJ Set</p>
<p>$300</p>
</div>

<div class="card">
<h3>Club / Event Package</h3>
<p>4 Hour DJ Set + Lighting</p>
<p>$700</p>
</div>

<div class="card">
<h3>Wedding Package</h3>
<p>Full Reception DJ + MC</p>
<p>$1200</p>
</div>

</section>

<section id="booking">
<h2>Book Me</h2>

<div class="card">

<form>

<input placeholder="Name">

<input placeholder="Email">

<input placeholder="Event Type">

<input placeholder="Event Date">

<textarea placeholder="Event Details"></textarea>

<button type="submit">Submit Booking</button>

</form>

</div>

</section>

<section id="payments">
<h2>Payments</h2>

<div class="card">

<p>You can send deposits or full payments via:</p>

<p>
PayPal: yourpaypal@email.com <br>
CashApp: $YourDJName <br>
Venmo: @YourName
</p>

</div>

</section>

<section id="support">
<h2>Support / Tips</h2>

<div class="card">

<p>If you enjoy my mixes you can support with tips ❤️</p>

<button>Send Tip</button>

</div>

</section>

<section id="contact">
<h2>Contact</h2>

<div class="card">

<p>Email: booking@djname.com</p>

<p>Instagram DM is also open for bookings.</p>

</div>

</section>

<footer>
<p>© 2026 DJ YourName</p>
</footer>

</body>
</html>
